Installing your dish. Even if you are capable of tuning your TV and configuring your set-top box, putting up a satellite dish requires some expertise and equipment. Like analogue satellite TV before it, digital satellite television requires a relatively small satellite dish that serves just your household.Some are designed to receive signals from just one satellite, others are designed to handle several satellites.ike analogue satellite TV before it, digital satellite television requires a relatively small satellite dish that serves just your household. Some are designed to receive signals from just one satellite, others are designed to handle several satellites.
